{"tid":2511161,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"緬甸多座城市爆發反軍方遊行示威","createTime":"2021-04-30T16:35:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T02:10:47.000Z","uid":184679,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"906d7e63c9d3c908b4fa22765cf6f97dd22abb12","tid":2511161,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T16:35:12.000Z","msg":"當地時間4月30日，緬甸的仰光、曼德勒、毛淡棉、德拜因、帕敢等多座城市爆發遊行示威，反對軍方接管政權，並對此前剛剛成立的民族團結政府表示支持。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.mix.sina.com.cn/auto/resize?img=%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fspider2021430%2F550%2Fw800h550%2F20210430%2F43c6-kpptear6660081.jpg&amp;size=640_0&amp;blur=1&amp;blur_sigma=2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.mix.sina.com.cn%2Fauto%2Fresize%3Fimg%3D%252F%252Fn.sinaimg.cn%252Fspider2021430%252F550%252Fw800h550%252F20210430%252F43c6-kpptear6660081.jpg%26size%3D640_0%26blur%3D1%26blur_sigma%3D2&h=0f0a6af4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.mix.sina.com.cn/auto/resize?img=%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fspider20210430%2F717%2Fw893h624%2F20210430%2F6950-kpptear6660403.jpg&amp;size=640_0&amp;blur=1&amp;blur_sigma=2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.mix.sina.com.cn%2Fauto%2Fresize%3Fimg%3D%252F%252Fn.sinaimg.cn%252Fspider20210430%252F717%252Fw893h624%252F20210430%252F6950-kpptear6660403.jpg%26size%3D640_0%26blur%3D1%26blur_sigma%3D2&h=6eaf9a34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有些市民在凌晨就開始遊行示威，而在當天下著大雨的仰光等城市，示威者冒雨繼續遊行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.mix.sina.com.cn/auto/resize?img=%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fspider2021430%2F80%2Fw960h720%2F20210430%2Fd297-kpptear6660148.jpg&amp;size=640_0&amp;blur=1&amp;blur_sigma=2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.mix.sina.com.cn%2Fauto%2Fresize%3Fimg%3D%252F%252Fn.sinaimg.cn%252Fspider2021430%252F80%252Fw960h720%252F20210430%252Fd297-kpptear6660148.jpg%26size%3D640_0%26blur%3D1%26blur_sigma%3D2&h=ea4b4d55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.mix.sina.com.cn/auto/resize?img=%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fspider2021430%2F80%2Fw960h720%2F20210430%2Fe598-kpptear6660147.jpg&amp;size=640_0&amp;blur=1&amp;blur_sigma=2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.mix.sina.com.cn%2Fauto%2Fresize%3Fimg%3D%252F%252Fn.sinaimg.cn%252Fspider2021430%252F80%252Fw960h720%252F20210430%252Fe598-kpptear6660147.jpg%26size%3D640_0%26blur%3D1%26blur_sigma%3D2&h=804a9633&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當天下午，部分地區的警方對遊行示威者進行了驅散和抓捕，其中在仰光南德貢鎮區，有4名示威者被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://news.sina. cn/gn/2021-04-30/detail-ikmxzfmk9966280 .d.html?from=wap</code></pre>"},{"pid":"7a58ca1cd1a463df7667dc305e15499dcfdc6a40","tid":2511161,"uid":280329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T16:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81345162d3a662f0bf1d3e13d886bffda922ac64","tid":2511161,"uid":34213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T16:44:13.000Z","msg":"拳頭夠大先有資格決定和平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc7a4fd66f899c2be8fc199329511da8bb0a325","tid":2511161,"uid":115579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T17:22:28.000Z","msg":"地方大就算拉都冇咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6d077341a821a2939174ddc60ece14d4a8e3b3","tid":2511161,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdc7a4fd66f899c2be8fc199329511da8bb0a325","tid":2511161,"uid":115579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T17:22:28.000Z","msg":"地方大就算拉都冇咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T17:23:17.000Z","msg":"更何況有軍隊"},{"pid":"8fc2da606517e0658403c0a5a41f901ea7b96226","tid":2511161,"uid":105924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-